00:00:03.567 --> 00:00:15.801
Face yourself for becoming.

00:00:15.801 --> 00:00:32.934
Then the preparation is done to become something

00:00:32.934 --> 00:00:42.834
and on the whole, when you know that it is
your ego and superego which are loading you up,

00:00:42.834 --> 00:00:53.134
you have to scan them out with vibratory awareness.

00:00:53.134 --> 00:01:06.701
Now there are two types of attention we have to pay.

00:01:06.701 --> 00:01:13.901
First is a constant attention that is a routine of a Sahaja Yogi,

00:01:13.901 --> 00:01:22.934
and the second one is the emergency attention.

00:01:22.934 --> 00:01:31.401
I have been saying that all the Sahaja Yogis
must start writing their diaries:

00:01:31.401 --> 00:01:36.501
one with every day’s experiences,

00:01:36.501 --> 00:01:43.167
if you know that you have to write a diary,
you’ll keep your mind alert,

00:01:43.167 --> 00:01:49.734
and another whenever you get any special idea of the past or of the future,

00:01:49.734 --> 00:01:50.901
also to jot it down.

00:01:50.901 --> 00:01:54.501
So, like that, you should have two diaries.

00:01:54.501 --> 00:02:01.401
For your constant attention,
you have to fix up your mind on certain things.

00:02:01.401 --> 00:02:06.901
The first one, as I said, that if you keep a diary

00:02:06.901 --> 00:02:13.067
then you will know that you have to remember
what important things have happened.

00:02:13.067 --> 00:02:18.034
So your attention will be alert and
you will be looking out for such points,

00:02:18.034 --> 00:02:21.467
where, what is the thing you see.

00:02:21.467 --> 00:02:24.901
And you’ll be amazed, if you make your attention alert,

00:02:24.901 --> 00:02:29.501
what new things come to you -

00:02:29.501 --> 00:02:33.501
very brilliant ideas.

00:02:33.501 --> 00:02:42.034
And the miracles of life and the miracles of God’s beauty and His auspiciousness,

00:02:42.034 --> 00:02:45.501
His greatness, His kindness, His blessings -

00:02:45.501 --> 00:02:51.401
how they work out if you start writing every day even two lines about it.

00:02:51.401 --> 00:02:56.601
It will make your mind constantly involved with it.

00:02:56.601 --> 00:03:01.334
That’s a human style of doing things.

00:03:01.334 --> 00:03:08.501
Also you can mention in the diary

00:03:08.501 --> 00:03:11.501
what happened: did you, could you do your meditation?

00:03:11.501 --> 00:03:14.401
Did you get your time for meditation or not?

00:03:14.401 --> 00:03:21.901
A little bit as if you are appearing
for some sort of an examination or something,

00:03:21.901 --> 00:03:23.601
you prepare a little note like that:

00:03:23.601 --> 00:03:27.801
“Did I get up in the morning? Did I?”

00:03:27.801 --> 00:03:36.401
Then any special path or any special movement

00:03:36.401 --> 00:03:39.467
in the centre or left or right also should be mentioned

00:03:39.467 --> 00:03:42.167
so that you keep a watch on your mind.

00:03:42.167 --> 00:03:46.134
It’s a very good thing to maintain a diary.

00:03:46.134 --> 00:03:51.801
Also, you will see progressively how your ideas are changing,

00:03:51.801 --> 00:03:54.734
how new priorities are settling down,

00:03:54.734 --> 00:03:59.367
how you give more importance to real things

00:03:59.367 --> 00:04:04.667
and very little to unreal things.

00:04:04.667 --> 00:04:08.234
I think this is a very, very practical side of human beings

00:04:08.234 --> 00:04:10.901
that one should have a diary.

00:04:10.901 --> 00:04:16.401
Same diaries, after some time, will become historical things

00:04:16.401 --> 00:04:20.467
and people would like to see what you all have written.

00:04:20.467 --> 00:04:26.201
Not to be hypocritical about it or deceptive about it,

00:04:26.201 --> 00:04:30.501
but quite truthful and understanding.

00:04:30.501 --> 00:04:38.667
You should jot down few lines just before sleeping.

00:04:38.667 --> 00:04:47.334
Now we have to see that
we have problems for superego and ego.

00:04:47.334 --> 00:04:51.834
Now superego is the left side, is darkness,

00:04:51.834 --> 00:04:56.801
tamo guna and our past.

00:04:56.801 --> 00:05:01.401
Those who have left side problems should think of the future,

00:05:01.401 --> 00:05:05.401
it gives them balancing if they think of the future.

00:05:05.401 --> 00:05:15.401
For example, a person who is lethargic should take to working.

00:05:15.401 --> 00:05:18.701
Put your mind into working for the future planning:

00:05:18.701 --> 00:05:21.901
what to do, where to go, how to do.

00:05:21.901 --> 00:05:30.167
That will keep you away from drag of the left side

00:05:30.167 --> 00:05:40.401
and gradually then you can balance yourself also.

00:05:40.401 --> 00:05:52.601
Now the right side of a person, when it is activated very much,

00:05:52.601 --> 00:06:01.734
he has to balance it not with the left side but with the centre.

00:06:01.734 --> 00:06:09.567
That is, a person who is very hard-working

00:06:09.567 --> 00:06:14.801
must develop a witness state.

00:06:14.801 --> 00:06:19.801
You try to do a work, any work,

00:06:19.801 --> 00:06:28.000
indulge into work in thoughtless awareness, as a witness.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:35.067
Whatever work you are doing you just say that:
“I am not doing it."

00:06:35.067 --> 00:06:37.701
This You can do it after Realisation.

00:06:37.701 --> 00:06:42.834
You become thoughtlessly aware and start doing your work.

00:06:42.834 --> 00:06:47.801
So the compensation of the left side is done by movement to the right,

00:06:47.801 --> 00:06:50.701
and of the right side [by] movement in the centre.

00:06:50.701 --> 00:06:54.401
Left side is the tamo guna, right side is the rajo guna,

00:06:54.401 --> 00:06:59.701
the centre is the sattwo guna.
But still these are three gunas.

00:06:59.701 --> 00:07:03.301
That’s not the state which we have to achieve.

00:07:03.301 --> 00:07:08.934
About this I’ll tell you tomorrow more,
how to go further then.

00:07:08.934 --> 00:07:13.401
After scanning out which side is weak,

00:07:13.401 --> 00:07:17.667
you should plan out your style of life.

00:07:17.667 --> 00:07:22.401
For example, if you are extremely lethargic,
you cannot get up in the morning,

00:07:22.401 --> 00:07:26.701
you feel very sleepy in the night, you do not feel alerted

00:07:26.701 --> 00:07:31.000
then start planning as to what will you do.
How will you get up?

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:33.801
Even puja is a good idea, homa (havan) is a good idea.

00:07:33.801 --> 00:07:37.601
Do something like that, so that you have to do something,

00:07:37.601 --> 00:07:41.667
what you call the kriya, is the action,
get into the action.

00:07:41.667 --> 00:07:49.734
Some sort of action you go into in Sahaja Yoga as well as in your daily life

00:07:49.734 --> 00:07:54.301
you’ll be able to change that mood and come to the right side

00:07:54.301 --> 00:07:59.501
and then you’ll go to the,
your movement should be towards the sattwa guna,

00:07:59.501 --> 00:08:03.501
is to watch everything.

00:08:03.501 --> 00:08:09.901
Now at the sattwa guna point where you are in the centre

00:08:09.901 --> 00:08:17.501
you have to see how much you are misidentified.

00:08:17.501 --> 00:08:24.034
Say, supposing you are at the first stage of left side,

00:08:24.034 --> 00:08:29.167
then you will just do daydreaming,
“Oh! This person is so much identified,

00:08:29.167 --> 00:08:32.000
that one is so much identified,” as if you are the best.

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:34.301
It’s just human nature, you see.

00:08:34.301 --> 00:08:36.701
“Oh, that person is like that, he is like that,

00:08:36.701 --> 00:08:41.701
this is very bad in the society,
that is going bad in the society. It’s better…”

00:08:41.701 --> 00:08:45.334
Then we can also go to this limit is to,
“That guru is very bad

00:08:45.334 --> 00:08:49.334
and that one is another madcap."
Like that, you see, all daydreaming going on.

00:08:49.334 --> 00:08:51.000
How far it is affecting you,

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:53.034
how far are you improving by that is not…

00:08:53.034 --> 00:08:58.134
It’s just, you see, thinking, analysing.
It is, it's a lazy stuf,

00:08:58.134 --> 00:09:01.801
sitting down and just analysing, it's a lazy stuff.

00:09:01.801 --> 00:09:04.834
The second thing could be

00:09:04.834 --> 00:09:08.701
when you come to the second side of it, is the kriya.

00:09:08.701 --> 00:09:16.567
Then what happens when you start doing it,
then at least your attention is on what you are doing.

00:09:16.567 --> 00:09:20.801
It’s not allowed to drift into something
and which goes into any nonsense and can,

00:09:20.801 --> 00:09:25.134
I mean, then you don’t know from where the funny thoughts are coming.

00:09:25.134 --> 00:09:26.701
So, you start doing something.

00:09:26.701 --> 00:09:31.801
You can go and plant some trees
or you can go and plant some flowers

00:09:31.801 --> 00:09:34.734
or if you want you can do some cooking, you can do some work.

00:09:34.734 --> 00:09:39.167
Take to work! That will help you. Any work.

00:09:39.167 --> 00:09:44.467
But while doing the work the problem will be, you’ll develop ego.

00:09:44.467 --> 00:09:50.234
That’s why when you are developing the ego you have to tell yourself,

00:09:50.234 --> 00:09:53.367
“You are not doing, mister! This you are not doing,

00:09:53.367 --> 00:09:55.601
this is not doing, you are not doing.”

00:09:55.601 --> 00:09:57.701
If you go on suggesting to yourself,

00:09:57.701 --> 00:09:59.901
Mr. Ego will not come up.

00:09:59.901 --> 00:10:03.401
And then many things, you see,
which normally trouble you and trouble others

00:10:03.401 --> 00:10:06.567
like you have cleaned the room, alright.

00:10:06.567 --> 00:10:10.801
Then somebody comes and spoils it
you get angry with that person.

00:10:10.801 --> 00:10:14.401
Naturally! Because you think ‘you’ have done.

00:10:14.401 --> 00:10:17.834
First of all you don’t clean the room.
If you clean the room then you are prepared,

00:10:17.834 --> 00:10:22.601
it will be dirty, otherwise why should you clean?

00:10:22.601 --> 00:10:25.101
Now, if it is dirty, well and good;

00:10:25.101 --> 00:10:29.401
if it is not dirty, well and good.

00:10:29.401 --> 00:10:34.934
This type of attitude you should take to jump onto sattva guna.

00:10:34.934 --> 00:10:38.301
On sattva guna you start accepting it.

00:10:38.301 --> 00:10:43.701
You become extremely mild.
You become a mild personality.

00:10:43.701 --> 00:10:49.167
Then at that time you do not discuss as to, “Oh, I don’t like it;

00:10:49.167 --> 00:10:51.467
this was wrong; this should not have been."

00:10:51.467 --> 00:10:54.101
All these things do not come to you in sattva guna.

00:10:54.101 --> 00:10:58.067
You start seeing it. That time you see it

00:10:58.067 --> 00:11:01.134
that, “Alright, doesn’t matter.
It’s done, it’s done.”

00:11:01.134 --> 00:11:05.501
On the contrary, you feel hurt if you are a sattwa guni,

00:11:05.501 --> 00:11:12.667
that by any suggestion you have suggested your ego.

00:11:12.667 --> 00:11:15.101
Can you get that point?

00:11:15.101 --> 00:11:19.101
You feel ashamed of your ego,
I mean to say, if you are a sattwa guni.

00:11:19.101 --> 00:11:25.301
For example, even to say that “This is my car,”
you will feel shy. That’s a sattwa guni type.

00:11:25.301 --> 00:11:27.601
Or even to say, “Why did you spoil my carpet?”

00:11:27.601 --> 00:11:30.167
I mean in India nobody will say,
I can tell you this!

00:11:30.167 --> 00:11:33.101
Is regarded [as] bad manners, absolute bad manners.

00:11:33.101 --> 00:11:36.367
If anybody comes to your house and the carpet
is spoiled they say, “Let it be, doesn’t matter."

00:11:36.367 --> 00:11:40.834
Even it is burnt, “I don’t know. Let it be. Are you burnt?”

00:11:40.834 --> 00:11:44.401
They’ll never say that, “You have burnt my carpet,
or done anything to my…”

00:11:44.401 --> 00:11:47.134
Is regarded bad manners.

00:11:47.134 --> 00:11:52.134
Like here, you see, if somebody’s sleeping
somebody makes the noise.

00:11:52.134 --> 00:11:57.167
The person who is sleeping will never say that
“You are making noise,

00:11:57.167 --> 00:12:02.167
He’ll just get up and ask,
“Do you need anything?”

00:12:02.167 --> 00:12:04.601
That’s difficult for people here to understand

00:12:04.601 --> 00:12:09.401
because ego is just sitting on the head.
But is bad manners there.

00:12:09.401 --> 00:12:12.501
You will find when you’ll go to India you’ll find this.

00:12:12.501 --> 00:12:18.401
These are bad manners to say that.
Or to say, “Oh, I, I feel very comfortable.

00:12:18.401 --> 00:12:21.201
I mean, to say “I feel comfortable” is bad manners.

00:12:21.201 --> 00:12:24.701
I mean, they never say “I like it.”

00:12:24.701 --> 00:12:28.134
“So what?” All these words are not to be said.

00:12:28.134 --> 00:12:31.401
If you are a sattwa guni then you just don’t say,

00:12:31.401 --> 00:12:38.067
you will say, “Do you like it?
Is it comfortable? Would you like to have this?”

00:12:38.067 --> 00:12:47.067
The whole attention goes from your side.
Do you understand that?

00:12:47.067 --> 00:12:50.901
That is the style one has to develop.
Then you are a sattwa guni.

00:12:50.901 --> 00:12:54.167
Otherwise, you are still on ego trip.
You see, whatever you may think,

00:12:54.167 --> 00:13:00.401
“I don’t like that, I don’t…”
“I”- who are you?

00:13:00.401 --> 00:13:03.501
First of all, ask the question, “Who are you?”

00:13:03.501 --> 00:13:08.801
If God says, “I don’t like you,”
I can understand, with good reasons,

00:13:08.801 --> 00:13:11.134
but for you to say, “I don’t like it” …

00:13:11.134 --> 00:13:16.901
After all, how did you come on this earth?

00:13:16.901 --> 00:13:20.401
How did you get a human birth?

00:13:20.401 --> 00:13:24.801
How did you get all these things?
Now think like that.

00:13:24.801 --> 00:13:30.101
“Who am I?"

00:13:30.101 --> 00:13:33.101
"I am nothing."

00:13:33.101 --> 00:13:37.667
Anybody who thinks, “I am something,”
he should know that he’s nothing;

00:13:37.667 --> 00:13:45.801
makes no difference to God whether he exists or
does not exist, you see, he’s nothing, he’s just a drop.

00:13:45.801 --> 00:13:48.467
So, this point if you understand,

00:13:48.467 --> 00:13:50.067
that even if you do something,

00:13:50.067 --> 00:13:53.134
any work you do or anything you are doing,

00:13:53.134 --> 00:14:01.167
you are just doing it because you want to do it.

00:14:01.167 --> 00:14:04.467
That is how you come on to sattva guna.

00:14:04.467 --> 00:14:07.701
But normally it doesn’t happen.
It happens the other way round.

00:14:07.701 --> 00:14:17.234
For example, a person is, say, doing something

00:14:17.234 --> 00:14:19.534
by any chance he feels hurt

00:14:19.534 --> 00:14:22.134
or he thinks that whatever he has done is no good.

00:14:22.134 --> 00:14:25.367
People don’t appreciate,
or maybe he might think that,

00:14:25.367 --> 00:14:29.667
“Oh, it’s not up to the point,” or whatever it is,

00:14:29.667 --> 00:14:33.934
then the reaction for him is not that
he does not try to rise to sattva guna,

00:14:33.934 --> 00:14:39.367
but he goes back to tamo guna.

00:14:39.367 --> 00:14:44.867
“Alright, I’ll not do it. I’ll sleep over it.
Let them do it, why should I do it?”

00:14:44.867 --> 00:14:52.101
So the training that you have to have
through your rajo guna goes a waste.

00:14:52.101 --> 00:14:56.434
It’s just a training period that you are with rajo guna.

00:14:56.434 --> 00:14:57.934
You are doing something.

00:14:57.934 --> 00:15:05.734
Now in that training period you have to learn
only how to come in the centre.

00:15:05.734 --> 00:15:13.734
For example, now, water is required for you to swim.
If there is no water you cannot swim.

00:15:13.734 --> 00:15:20.834
All right? In the same way, rajo guna is required for you to come to sattwa guni.

00:15:20.834 --> 00:15:26.034
If you do not do any work you cannot come to sattwa guna.

00:15:26.034 --> 00:15:31.534
So you are just working just to train yourself to be a witness.

00:15:31.534 --> 00:15:33.267
Now do you follow that point?

00:15:33.267 --> 00:15:36.301
You are not doing it because you like particular thing,

00:15:36.301 --> 00:15:39.134
you are used to particular thing, because you want to be this.

00:15:39.134 --> 00:15:43.201
This is not the way it is.

00:15:43.201 --> 00:15:48.201
You are just doing it to learn how to be patient.

00:15:48.201 --> 00:15:54.734
To practice your patience.
To see how much patient, you are.

00:15:54.734 --> 00:15:57.967
Once you start doing it, you’ll be amazed

00:15:57.967 --> 00:16:03.334
that you will never feel the burden of the work.

00:16:03.334 --> 00:16:05.734
But it never happens.

00:16:05.734 --> 00:16:13.067
Most of the people, if they find their work is
not effective, they’ll go back to tamo guna.

00:16:13.067 --> 00:16:15.734
There are many attitudes.
Say, somebody’s working,

00:16:15.734 --> 00:16:19.334
then he thinks, “Why should I do all the work?
Others are not doing!”

00:16:19.334 --> 00:16:23.867
He’ll go back to their stage.
But those who are not working will not think that,

00:16:23.867 --> 00:16:27.234
“This person is working, let me also work.”

00:16:27.234 --> 00:16:30.634
It’s other way round, you see.

00:16:30.634 --> 00:16:32.701
This can be an attitude of some people that

00:16:32.701 --> 00:16:38.634
“if this person is working, let him work."

00:16:38.634 --> 00:16:42.967
This is even a meaner stuff, avoid, just.

00:16:42.967 --> 00:16:46.101
You go to a restaurant and
somebody takes out the purse,

00:16:46.101 --> 00:16:49.534
others start looking this side – is very mean,

00:16:49.534 --> 00:16:54.601
it’s a very mean thing to do.
Everybody should come forward

00:16:54.601 --> 00:16:56.901
and once you have paid, you have paid it, finished.

00:16:56.901 --> 00:17:01.134
Then you just don’t start counting,
“Why did I pay?”

00:17:01.134 --> 00:17:05.801
Once you try Or any work has to be done,

00:17:05.801 --> 00:17:09.067
go forward with it, do it with your heart.

00:17:09.067 --> 00:17:12.467
Don’t worry if others have not done it.

00:17:12.467 --> 00:17:16.067
Just do it for its pleasure and
the pleasure only you will get

00:17:16.067 --> 00:17:20.367
when you will do it with the understanding that it’s a training period,

00:17:20.367 --> 00:17:25.000
you are better trained than the other one is.

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:27.567
You are at a higher class than the other one is.

00:17:27.567 --> 00:17:32.701
So we have to be at a higher class.

00:17:32.701 --> 00:17:36.101
For that this is just a training on.

00:17:36.101 --> 00:17:43.534
And that’s how we can really put our preparation into practice, into all details

00:17:43.534 --> 00:17:48.734
to see how we work out our ego and superego.

00:17:48.734 --> 00:17:57.000
Today, in the morning, I have told you that your intellect must imbibe this within itself, all right?

00:17:57.000 --> 00:18:05.401
And now I’m telling you that your action,
action that you do,

00:18:05.401 --> 00:18:20.234
must be every time branded by you
as just your training – any action you do.

00:18:20.234 --> 00:18:23.601
Supposing you have to drive for miles together,

00:18:23.601 --> 00:18:25.401
you are trying your patience.

00:18:25.401 --> 00:18:29.901
You see they’ll do in everything.
Say they have to go for say helicopter,

00:18:29.901 --> 00:18:35.067
or say if they have to drop from the…
what you call them, they drop down?

00:18:35.067 --> 00:18:36.634
Sahaja Yogis: Parachutes.

00:18:36.634 --> 00:18:37.234
Ha?

00:18:37.234 --> 00:18:39.167
Shri Mataji: Parachuters!

00:18:39.167 --> 00:18:42.567
Or helicopter you take away or whatever it is.

00:18:42.567 --> 00:18:47.234
You go on doing it again and again, isn’t it?
You practice it again and again.

00:18:47.234 --> 00:18:50.134
You drop many-a-times, you break your legs, you break your hands,

00:18:50.134 --> 00:18:56.701
you do this and do that till you become a master.
You understand My point?

00:18:56.701 --> 00:18:59.867
Driving – same way, till you become a master, you go on.

00:18:59.867 --> 00:19:05.667
In the same way, you are doing this work
just to master your patience.

00:19:05.667 --> 00:19:13.034
And then your love, is your love –
how much you love really.

00:19:13.034 --> 00:19:20.867
If you really love someone,
you are never tired of working.

00:19:20.867 --> 00:19:23.701
You are never upset with work.

00:19:23.701 --> 00:19:26.701
But if you don’t love, you start counting,

00:19:26.701 --> 00:19:32.767
“How much money, how much work,
how many hours, how much to be paid?”

00:19:32.767 --> 00:19:38.901
All artificiality comes because
there is no love involved in your work.

00:19:38.901 --> 00:19:45.334
Whatever you don’t want to do, you don’t do it, to begin with.

00:19:45.334 --> 00:19:51.367
To begin with you just don’t do
what you don’t like – to begin with.

00:19:51.367 --> 00:19:53.734
But once you have mastered that,

00:19:53.734 --> 00:19:59.334
then you have to master it that
you do something that you don’t like.

00:19:59.334 --> 00:20:02.334
Like meeting some bhooties, for example.

00:20:02.334 --> 00:20:05.767
You don’t want to meet, you want to run away,

00:20:05.767 --> 00:20:09.067
but you go little nearer it, you see.

00:20:09.067 --> 00:20:11.667
Then develop a immunity for these bhooties.

00:20:11.667 --> 00:20:16.067
After some time you’ll not catch them.

00:20:16.067 --> 00:20:18.801
We have to develop the immunity, isn’t it?

00:20:18.801 --> 00:20:24.701
Otherwise one person comes here and everybody’s head goes out.

00:20:24.701 --> 00:20:28.867
Instead of the fellow improving, you all go out.

00:20:28.867 --> 00:20:36.767
So all these things are, all these events
are for your training, your immunity.

00:20:36.767 --> 00:20:41.367
Your immunity is to be trained

00:20:41.367 --> 00:20:43.901
and when it is so, when we are training ourselves

00:20:43.901 --> 00:20:48.801
we should take it as a job.

00:20:48.801 --> 00:20:54.901
But the attitude should be extremely positive,

00:20:54.901 --> 00:20:58.067
extremely positive

00:20:58.067 --> 00:21:03.734
and all that should be expressed in your notebook:

00:21:03.734 --> 00:21:08.601
whether you got dejected or you got upset and disgusted,

00:21:08.601 --> 00:21:12.867
you want to run away from it – all sorts of things.

00:21:12.867 --> 00:21:19.167
It’s just a training to your mind.

00:21:19.167 --> 00:21:24.134
Whatever is the situation, wherever one has to live,

00:21:24.134 --> 00:21:30.567
whatever one has to do, we should do.

00:21:30.567 --> 00:21:35.334
Whatever may be the circumstances, conditions,

00:21:35.334 --> 00:21:38.567
you’ll be amazed, you will not even know
what you have eaten in the morning,

00:21:38.567 --> 00:21:43.767
what you have eaten in the evening,
whether you have eaten or not you will not know.

00:21:43.767 --> 00:21:47.167
You’ll not fuss about it,

00:21:47.167 --> 00:21:53.067
you’ll not worry about it, you’ll not think about it.

00:21:53.067 --> 00:22:01.367
But this being, the aim, is to reach to sattwa guna,

00:22:01.367 --> 00:22:07.067
every other thing becomes zero.

00:22:07.067 --> 00:22:10.601
It’s the greatest hurdle comes to Sahaja Yogis I’ve seen,

00:22:10.601 --> 00:22:14.434
when they start organising.

00:22:14.434 --> 00:22:19.034
They start organising something.
Now somebody wants something,

00:22:19.034 --> 00:22:23.034
so they’ll run up to get the thing for that person.

00:22:23.034 --> 00:22:27.000
Now just now I’ve said that you must look after the needs of others,

00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:33.000
but if I am sitting here and there’s a lecture on
then you’d better be just listening to Me.

00:22:33.000 --> 00:22:37.034
You see, this also is there that:
how to have your priorities,

00:22:37.034 --> 00:22:42.167
at this time when something working on you.

00:22:42.167 --> 00:22:45.000
This is the first thing you have to do.

00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:50.334
Not that at this time you go and cook.

00:22:50.334 --> 00:22:56.901
You have known the story of two sisters
attending on Christ. Alright?

00:22:56.901 --> 00:23:02.667
So at this time, what is your first job

00:23:02.667 --> 00:23:07.101
is to try to be more exposed to Me

00:23:07.101 --> 00:23:10.334
so that automatically you’ll go into your sattwa guna.

00:23:10.334 --> 00:23:13.234
This is the best!

00:23:13.234 --> 00:23:20.767
But if I am not there and when you are alone or when you are with other Sahaja Yogis

00:23:20.767 --> 00:23:25.767
you must now compete in rising higher and higher:

00:23:25.767 --> 00:23:30.434
from tamo guna to rajo guna and
from rajo guna to sattwo guna.

00:23:30.434 --> 00:23:35.734
But actually by Realisation
you have gone beyond these three gunas.

00:23:35.734 --> 00:23:42.501
You have gone beyond it.
Actually that is what has happened to you.

00:23:42.501 --> 00:23:48.634
But, like clouds, they cover you again and again.

00:23:48.634 --> 00:23:53.034
And when the sky is covered with those clouds,

00:23:53.034 --> 00:23:59.167
you cannot see the sun, you cannot see the moon,
you cannot see the stars.

00:23:59.167 --> 00:24:02.867
So we have to know how these clouds are coming into us

00:24:02.867 --> 00:24:06.734
and that’s how we go into our complete analysis.

00:24:06.734 --> 00:24:09.401
How these clouds are coming to us,

00:24:09.401 --> 00:24:13.701
you find out about our different chakras.

00:24:13.701 --> 00:24:17.967
What are the chakras we are catching?

00:24:17.967 --> 00:24:24.634
Here comes the another constant attention towards our chakras.

00:24:24.634 --> 00:24:30.801
Are our vibrations alright or not?
Are we getting our vibrations?

00:24:30.801 --> 00:24:35.734
If not, what chakra am I catching,
what must be the catch?

00:24:35.734 --> 00:24:40.367
I must raise my Kundalini, see for myself,
where is the catch.

00:24:40.367 --> 00:24:42.534
Do I do my meditation or not?

00:24:42.534 --> 00:24:47.634
If I do it, am I doing it just dozingly or am I really in it?

00:24:47.634 --> 00:24:52.501
Am I really feeling it or not? Am I alert or not?

00:24:52.501 --> 00:25:01.034
All this is to be assiduously, sincerely, absolutely, truthfully should be worked out.

00:25:01.034 --> 00:25:06.334
Because it is a process between your self

00:25:06.334 --> 00:25:08.834
"Atamanyeva Atmana tushta"
[The Spirit is satisfied with Itself].

00:25:08.834 --> 00:25:13.334
You see it’s a very funny, it is so funny relationship

00:25:13.334 --> 00:25:21.034
that it is the Atma is satisfied with Atma!

00:25:21.034 --> 00:25:24.767
You have to be satisfied with your Self.

00:25:24.767 --> 00:25:27.267
There’s nobody, Mataji is not concerned,
nobody is concerned.

00:25:27.267 --> 00:25:32.601
It is you who is concerned with your Self.

00:25:32.601 --> 00:25:38.601
For example, you ask somebody and he says,
“I am like this, Mother."

00:25:38.601 --> 00:25:41.334
Now think that you are Mother,

00:25:41.334 --> 00:25:51.101
one personality, another is, say, Mr. Don or Kingsley or someone X. You are two personalities.

00:25:51.101 --> 00:25:57.634
So when you are telling your Self,
means that is Mataji, that, “I am not alright,”

00:25:57.634 --> 00:26:00.701
then Mataji must come up and say,
“What do you mean by this?

00:26:00.701 --> 00:26:08.167
Why should you say like that? What’s wrong?”

00:26:08.167 --> 00:26:17.267
When you say that to yourself which is outside,

00:26:17.267 --> 00:26:26.834
then the attention starts moving towards your Self which is Mataji and you start becoming that

00:26:26.834 --> 00:26:30.501
and you start seeing through your Atma.

00:26:30.501 --> 00:26:35.767
So your Atma is to be satisfied by your Atma only.

00:26:35.767 --> 00:26:37.501
There is nothing in between.

00:26:37.501 --> 00:26:42.601
It is you only in this dual personality
has to satisfy your Self.

00:26:42.601 --> 00:26:46.534
One is in ignorance, one is in knowledge.

00:26:46.534 --> 00:26:51.167
Now try to identify yourself with that Mataji, call it,

00:26:51.167 --> 00:26:58.967
or any Xyz whatever you call it, Atma.
And just for, just a drama, say.

00:26:58.967 --> 00:27:03.601
You just think that you are the Self, Spirit.

00:27:03.601 --> 00:27:08.201
So how will you address your Self? Let’s see.

00:27:08.201 --> 00:27:09.834
Supposing you have to sit in My seat,

00:27:09.834 --> 00:27:12.234
yes, take it like that, a position.

00:27:12.234 --> 00:27:16.301
And then you are sitting in front of Me also, alright?

00:27:16.301 --> 00:27:19.734
So you are sitting here and sitting there.
Take a position like that.

00:27:19.734 --> 00:27:22.734
Now you put up your Self in a drama
and you start addressing yourself,

00:27:22.734 --> 00:27:26.534
“So Bala, how are you?”

00:27:26.534 --> 00:27:33.367
so Bala says, “Better,”

00:27:33.367 --> 00:27:38.934
So if you are identified now with Mataji,

00:27:38.934 --> 00:27:42.634
gradually Bala will diminish, alright?

00:27:42.634 --> 00:27:46.334
But if you are still identified with Bala,

00:27:46.334 --> 00:27:50.301
he’ll grow and this will diminish.

00:27:50.301 --> 00:28:00.501
You have to try to address yourself as if you are Mataji.

00:28:00.501 --> 00:28:07.401
It’s a drama.
You sit before the mirror.

00:28:07.401 --> 00:28:10.767
In the mirror you see this outside of yours

00:28:10.767 --> 00:28:15.367
and here you are sitting, whatever you are, Mr. Don for example.

00:28:15.367 --> 00:28:18.967
Now Mr. Don is addressing the other Don there,

00:28:18.967 --> 00:28:22.501
and let him take up a role that, “I am the Spirit.”

00:28:22.501 --> 00:28:27.967
He’ll say, “I am the Spirit and I am eternal.
I am this.

00:28:27.967 --> 00:28:31.734
Nobody can destroy me.
I am above everything."

00:28:31.734 --> 00:28:36.134
That thing will go down.

00:28:36.134 --> 00:28:38.934
“I am a realised soul.
I know what Spirit is.

00:28:38.934 --> 00:28:46.301
What are you talking?” It will go down.

00:28:46.301 --> 00:28:51.867
This is how you start moving.

00:28:51.867 --> 00:28:56.967
But it is only possible that first you become a sattwa guni.

00:28:56.967 --> 00:29:01.101
If you are not a sattwa guni, with ego, “I am this,”

00:29:01.101 --> 00:29:05.534
then you become a guru and you start minting money!

00:29:05.534 --> 00:29:08.234
First the ego is to be brought down.

00:29:08.234 --> 00:29:14.167
If there is still ego, then without becoming Atma you become an ego.

00:29:14.167 --> 00:29:18.934
So first this journey should be brought in to the centre of sattwa guna.

00:29:18.934 --> 00:29:25.767
That is why I say that when you are talking or doing anything,

00:29:25.767 --> 00:29:32.834
you must know that it is your Spirit which is doing it.

00:29:32.834 --> 00:29:38.867
That’s how you put your Spirit in charge

00:29:38.867 --> 00:29:43.534
or say at the pedestal – first stage.

00:29:43.534 --> 00:29:47.467
Then when the Spirit is there, then from this stage to that stage,

00:29:47.467 --> 00:29:52.401
then you say that, “Now I am the Spirit."

00:29:52.401 --> 00:29:59.534
For example, if you have a prime minister and a deputy minister and a minister – three persons, alright?

00:29:59.534 --> 00:30:06.101
Now, if the prime minister is your Self

00:30:06.101 --> 00:30:09.667
and the minister has to become the prime minister,

00:30:09.667 --> 00:30:13.667
so he has to first become deputy minister.

00:30:13.667 --> 00:30:18.067
After becoming deputy minister he has to become prime minister;

00:30:18.067 --> 00:30:21.067
but deputy prime minister and then the prime minister.

00:30:21.067 --> 00:30:24.434
But supposing this fellow starts to jump over this,

00:30:24.434 --> 00:30:25.901
this will come up and hit him and he’ll say,

00:30:25.901 --> 00:30:31.067
“I’m the one!”
and this one is E-G-O.

00:30:31.067 --> 00:30:34.901
Do you understand My point?

00:30:34.901 --> 00:30:38.667
So you cannot surpass it.

00:30:38.667 --> 00:30:43.167
You have to merge this into this and then this into this.

00:30:43.167 --> 00:30:45.167
The movement has to be like that.

00:30:45.167 --> 00:30:50.801
But if you try to just become this, actually you will become this, not this,

00:30:50.801 --> 00:30:53.701
because you cannot become this.

00:30:53.701 --> 00:30:57.367
Do you understand My point?

00:30:57.367 --> 00:31:03.067
So, even when doing this exercise of sitting before a mirror

00:31:03.067 --> 00:31:08.267
and telling yourself that you are the Spirit,

00:31:08.267 --> 00:31:20.134
you are the part of Viraat, that you are the Ocean

00:31:20.134 --> 00:31:24.667
because your drop has fallen into the Ocean.

00:31:24.667 --> 00:31:29.267
Then you must know that your drop has fallen into the Ocean.

00:31:29.267 --> 00:31:33.201
That’s why you’ve become an Ocean.
If that stage is missing,

00:31:33.201 --> 00:31:39.534
then you’re saying that you are an Ocean is absolutely bombastic.

00:31:39.534 --> 00:31:43.934
And that is why one has to be very steady and careful,

00:31:43.934 --> 00:31:47.767
absolutely steady as far as dealing with oneself.

00:31:47.767 --> 00:31:51.334
Because you know how this intelligence can cheat you.

00:31:51.334 --> 00:31:56.467
So be very, very careful and when you are dealing with you,

00:31:56.467 --> 00:32:01.434
you must know that you have to first overcome this ego.

00:32:01.434 --> 00:32:03.567
The best thing to overcome ego

00:32:03.567 --> 00:32:06.101
is to change your language style,

00:32:06.101 --> 00:32:10.667
is to speak in the third person.
Is a very good way.

00:32:10.667 --> 00:32:13.667
Like you must say, when you are talking about yourself,

00:32:13.667 --> 00:32:20.101
“This Mataji won’t listen to Me.
This Mataji won’t do this,”

00:32:20.101 --> 00:32:25.467
you see, so what happens, this ‘Mataji’ means the ego part of it, you see.

00:32:25.467 --> 00:32:29.767
And once you start separating this Mataji away from yourself,

00:32:29.767 --> 00:32:33.667
then that ego Mataji disappears.
You understand?

00:32:33.667 --> 00:32:38.767
Like you can say, "This Bala is like that.
He won’t listen."

00:32:38.767 --> 00:32:43.834
So whatever the real Bala is left in you is alright.

00:32:43.834 --> 00:32:47.000
That’s how you get rid of your ego

00:32:47.000 --> 00:32:51.801
and by understanding your centres,
what you are catching, where you are catching,

00:32:51.801 --> 00:32:54.801
how you are catching;

00:32:54.801 --> 00:33:01.534
it would be very easy for you to get rid of your problems.

00:33:01.534 --> 00:33:04.534
Now, see what Sahaja Yogis do.

00:33:04.534 --> 00:33:06.867
Supposing there are five Sahaja Yogis sitting.

00:33:06.867 --> 00:33:09.767
I mean you know that I know about everyone, everything.

00:33:09.767 --> 00:33:14.201
I don’t have to ask, “Where is catching?”

00:33:14.201 --> 00:33:19.267
Now why do I ask? I show complete ignorance.

00:33:19.267 --> 00:33:22.467
Because perhaps I never catch also, to be very frank.

00:33:22.467 --> 00:33:27.367
But if I want to know where I’m catching
I can find out but I don’t want to.

00:33:27.367 --> 00:33:31.867
So what I say, “Alright, Chaya, tell Me where is he catching."

00:33:31.867 --> 00:33:35.234
At this time one attitude could be that,

00:33:35.234 --> 00:33:41.834
“I must tell, otherwise Mataji won’t know.”
This is very funny.

00:33:41.834 --> 00:33:48.767
The second one could be,
and the second one could be that,

00:33:48.767 --> 00:33:58.267
that, “I know where she is catching and, and I must tell,

00:33:58.267 --> 00:34:06.267
and Mataji also knows but She wants to test me.
So I should be careful."

00:34:06.267 --> 00:34:08.967
At this point people make mistakes.

00:34:08.967 --> 00:34:13.967
If I ask them, “Where is it catching?”

00:34:13.967 --> 00:34:26.501
“I am catching on left heart but very mildly!”
Finished then! You, you’ll get less marks.

00:34:26.501 --> 00:34:30.067
You get less marks.
You tell Me whatever you think,

00:34:30.067 --> 00:34:36.334
because at least you’re honest.
Whatever you think.

00:34:36.334 --> 00:34:39.167
Supposing the fellow is not catching heart

00:34:39.167 --> 00:34:43.667
but you are feeling the heart.
You say, “Heart” That’s being honest.

00:34:43.667 --> 00:34:46.667
Then I will tell you who is catching the heart.

00:34:46.667 --> 00:34:52.634
But if you are, “Perhaps yes, Mataji. No, Mataji,”

00:34:52.634 --> 00:34:58.201
then you get less marks.
It’s not a very good answer.

00:34:58.201 --> 00:35:01.967
“I am not alright, I don’t know,” that’s not a good answer.

00:35:01.967 --> 00:35:06.934
You have to tell Me who is catching where.

00:35:06.934 --> 00:35:11.134
Then you pay more attention that you have to pass this test.

00:35:11.134 --> 00:35:14.401
This is just testing. Why?

00:35:14.401 --> 00:35:17.167
Because tomorrow you have to give Realisation.

00:35:17.167 --> 00:35:22.667
You have to become the gurus.
You have to know all this.

00:35:22.667 --> 00:35:25.767
So this is all training period.

00:35:25.767 --> 00:35:29.567
I’m just training you by asking you to tell Me,

00:35:29.567 --> 00:35:34.167
but I have seen people even getting ego with this.
It’s surprisingly sometimes.

00:35:34.167 --> 00:35:39.401
That also gives the ego to people that I say,
“Alright, you tell Me where he is catching?”

00:35:39.401 --> 00:35:43.867
“I told correctly!” Finished!

00:35:43.867 --> 00:35:51.334
You see, it is just a very, very, I can say, razor stage I tell you,

00:35:51.334 --> 00:35:55.967
where one has to see clearly.
So be a simple person like children are.

00:35:55.967 --> 00:36:00.234
They just come.
This one, that one, finished.

00:36:00.234 --> 00:36:04.101
Then they’ll go and sit down,
“Now I’m tired, I’m sitting down!”

00:36:04.101 --> 00:36:08.534
They are not bothered that they should…

00:36:08.534 --> 00:36:12.467
they must say something or something show off, nothing.

00:36:12.467 --> 00:36:16.967
Whatever they see, they say.

00:36:16.967 --> 00:36:18.601
But only grownups will say that,

00:36:18.601 --> 00:36:22.767
“Maybe I’m catching, maybe it is his.
I don’t know.”

00:36:22.767 --> 00:36:25.734
All this is done by grownup people

00:36:25.734 --> 00:36:33.401
because still the sensitivity is alright but they are not sure of themselves.

00:36:33.401 --> 00:36:37.467
Children are very sure.
They are cocksure of everything.

00:36:37.467 --> 00:36:40.534
You ask them anything, they’ll tell you,
“Yes, this is this, this is this.”

00:36:40.534 --> 00:36:45.567
ولی شما از هر کسی بپرسید:
"این چه رنگی است؟"

00:36:45.567 --> 00:36:51.901
They’ll say, “Maybe green, maybe red.”

00:36:51.901 --> 00:36:57.000
Like we had one old gentleman, not very old, as old as Myself

00:36:57.000 --> 00:37:02.767
but he was to come to My house and he telephoned to Me.

00:37:02.767 --> 00:37:05.201
He said, “I want to come to Your house
so how should I come?”

00:37:05.201 --> 00:37:08.067
I said, “This place is Oxted, you can come there but

00:37:08.067 --> 00:37:11.567
if you don’t get a taxi then it’s very difficult, better come to Hurst Green."

00:37:11.567 --> 00:37:14.967
He said, “Where?”
I said, “Hurst Green.”

00:37:14.967 --> 00:37:20.167
So he said, “Hurst Blue?”
How he is saying blue to green, I don’t know.

00:37:20.167 --> 00:37:23.167
I said, “No, it’s Hurst Green.”

00:37:23.167 --> 00:37:29.367
He said, “What did you say?”
I said, “Hurst Green.”

00:37:29.367 --> 00:37:33.334
So he couldn’t understand.
“What is the second one?”

00:37:33.334 --> 00:37:52.767
I said, “What is the colour of the leaves?” He said, “Blue.”

00:37:52.767 --> 00:37:56.567
I said it to Gregoire, I said, “Now listen to him, what is he saying?

00:37:56.567 --> 00:38:00.434
Colour of the leaves is blue?”

00:38:00.434 --> 00:38:10.167
So, Gregoire lifted the phone he said,
“Alright, you come to Hurst Blue.”

00:38:10.167 --> 00:38:12.901
So he said, “Now at least…”
I said, “What are you telling?”

00:38:12.901 --> 00:38:17.067
He said, “Now he won’t come, Mother.
That botheration is gone.

00:38:17.067 --> 00:38:21.134
Such a confused personality, mixing between blue and green!

00:38:21.134 --> 00:38:27.101
You are fighting. That’s what it is.
The attention drifts.

00:38:27.101 --> 00:38:30.234
So try to see that if you are confused, there is confusion,

00:38:30.234 --> 00:38:34.334
clear it out by clearing out your chakras.

00:38:34.334 --> 00:38:36.267
Now every chakra,

00:38:36.267 --> 00:38:40.401
let’s have a little testing of it alright, let’s see?

00:38:40.401 --> 00:38:45.401
One by one. So who are going to answer
the questions? Let’s see.

00:38:45.401 --> 00:38:51.767
Simple questions. Not ‘Mastermind’
Very simple questions.

00:38:51.767 --> 00:38:56.634
Now, say your Hamsa Chakra is catching,
what should we do?

00:38:56.634 --> 00:39:01.567
Who will answer the question?

00:39:01.567 --> 00:39:06.534
Hamsa Chakra is catching, what should we do?
Let’s see, one by one.

00:39:06.534 --> 00:39:10.401
Sahaja Yogi: Hamsa, Hamsa.

00:39:10.401 --> 00:39:13.467
That’s the name of the chakra.

