01:02:33.734 --> 01:02:36.667
not to be Romeo and Juliet anymore.

01:02:36.667 --> 01:02:42.701
You better have your children. And then the children that will be born to Sahaja Yogis

01:02:42.701 --> 01:02:48.467
are going to be realized souls, a tremendous source of energy.

01:02:48.467 --> 01:02:53.067
That’s why you are married,
that’s why you are going to have children.

01:02:53.067 --> 01:02:56.601
Then look after your children with respect, regard.

01:02:56.601 --> 01:03:03.701
Don’t spoil them! And develop in that love of Sahaja Yoga.

01:03:03.701 --> 01:03:08.000
Now this started with our Hamsa Chakra.

01:03:08.000 --> 01:03:11.901
Now see the Hamsa Chakra is the left and the right.

01:03:11.901 --> 01:03:15.067
The left is the woman, the right is the man.

01:03:15.067 --> 01:03:17.167
They meet at Hamsa.

01:03:17.167 --> 01:03:23.167
So this is the wedding place of your left and right.

01:03:23.167 --> 01:03:29.134
If there is no balance between the two, there is a problem.

01:03:29.134 --> 01:03:34.801
They have to be equal.
But they are not similar.

01:03:34.801 --> 01:03:38.167
Left is left. Right is right.

01:03:38.167 --> 01:03:44.234
So the right must be on the right hand side,
left must be on the left hand side

01:03:44.234 --> 01:03:51.467
and here when they come, they marry,
and this is the point one must know

01:03:51.467 --> 01:03:56.467
that, whatever is the function of a wife is,
she should do that first

01:03:56.467 --> 01:04:01.701
whatever is the function of the husband is,
he should do that first.

01:04:01.701 --> 01:04:08.067
And then the secondary functions of life can be shared and understood.

01:04:08.067 --> 01:04:13.867
But it’s not possible that the wife goes to work and the husband starts producing children.

01:04:13.867 --> 01:04:18.267
You cannot do it!

01:04:18.267 --> 01:04:24.000
And the other way round.
So whatever is the work is so important.

01:04:24.000 --> 01:04:26.867
To be a mother, I think, is the most important.

01:04:26.867 --> 01:04:29.667
Today if you didn’t have a mother,

01:04:29.667 --> 01:04:32.201
which father would have done this work, you tell Me.

01:04:32.201 --> 01:04:34.967
Which one? Can you think of anyone?

01:04:34.967 --> 01:04:39.467
There may be ‘Father in Heaven’,
but Father on this Earth

01:04:39.467 --> 01:04:43.634
working with all Sahaja Yogis, let Me see which one is there.

01:04:43.634 --> 01:04:45.767
Anyone of these fathers, you call them.

01:04:45.767 --> 01:04:51.467
Nicely to sit down on Heaven and watch the whole stuff. But who’s going to do the work?

01:04:51.467 --> 01:04:58.534
Washing the dirty linen and washing all the napkins
and things is done by Mother.

01:04:58.534 --> 01:05:04.634
She does this with love and attention and with care,

01:05:04.634 --> 01:05:12.101
and She is the one who knows how to grow Her children. Is the job of a mother.

01:05:12.101 --> 01:05:13.767
So Mother’s job Mother can do.

01:05:13.767 --> 01:05:16.934
Father can sit in Heaven very nicely.

01:05:16.934 --> 01:05:18.667
All thanks goes to the Father.

01:05:18.667 --> 01:05:22.534
While the Mother is doing a thankless job here!

01:05:22.534 --> 01:05:24.767
Alright, doesn’t matter.

01:05:24.767 --> 01:05:28.967
It is so, so should be accepted,
whatever may be the situation,

01:05:28.967 --> 01:05:33.367
whatever may be the position.

01:05:33.367 --> 01:05:37.734
Now at Hamsa Chakra, this understanding must come

01:05:37.734 --> 01:05:44.534
that you must balance both the nadis, the left and the right.

01:05:44.534 --> 01:05:50.301
Now to balance the left and the right,
the best way is to do some breathing,

01:05:50.301 --> 01:05:57.901
is to take the air through one nostril
and keep it waiting here for a while

01:05:57.901 --> 01:06:00.667
and then allow it to go out of the other.

01:06:00.667 --> 01:06:02.567
Then you breathe in with this one,

01:06:02.567 --> 01:06:06.867
allow it to stay here for a while and
then allow it to go down.

01:06:06.867 --> 01:06:10.067
But it is to be done very slowly.

01:06:10.067 --> 01:06:14.067
Not in a hurry, not too much.
Only thrice.

01:06:14.067 --> 01:06:16.167
Best thing as I’ve told you is neti.

01:06:16.167 --> 01:06:23.000
If not that, another thing I have seen that those inhalers, you see that you get, are very good.

01:06:23.000 --> 01:06:32.534
The neti thing that I’ve given you.
If you fill the water below the spout and fill it,

01:06:32.534 --> 01:06:37.967
put in some two, three drops of one of those things
that you get for inhaling

01:06:37.967 --> 01:06:44.234
and put that neti thing in one nose only,
and with another nose it goes up.

01:06:44.234 --> 01:06:47.867
Then you come, bring it here, it goes up and clears it out.

01:06:47.867 --> 01:06:49.801
It’s a very good thing.

01:06:49.801 --> 01:06:56.534
If you do it every night before sleeping,
in three, four days you’ll be absolutely cleared out.

01:06:56.534 --> 01:07:01.401
But the main thing is: it comes because of imbalances in our temperaments.

01:07:01.401 --> 01:07:04.167
Like a man is a man, woman is a woman, alright,

01:07:04.167 --> 01:07:09.967
so the woman starts dominating a man
or a man starts dominating the woman.

01:07:09.967 --> 01:07:14.767
The balance is broken.
Once you understand the woman is very important

01:07:14.767 --> 01:07:17.867
without the woman you cannot, could not have been here.
Alright?

01:07:17.867 --> 01:07:20.634
Without a woman you cannot be here.

01:07:20.634 --> 01:07:25.634
Man is very important that a woman has no meaning without a man.

01:07:25.634 --> 01:07:31.067
You see, Shakti has no meaning without God.
For whom is She working?

01:07:31.067 --> 01:07:34.567
For whom is She doing all this? For God to be pleased.

01:07:34.567 --> 01:07:37.534
If there’s nobody to see the job, why should She do it?

01:07:37.534 --> 01:07:40.467
So both have great meaning.
And if you understand

01:07:40.467 --> 01:07:45.567
that both beings within us are balanced, understood, respected

01:07:45.567 --> 01:07:49.301
in their proper ways

01:07:49.301 --> 01:08:04.701
and shared and coordinated, the personalities
in proper understanding, respect and love,

01:08:04.701 --> 01:08:09.234
your Hamsa will be alright.
You’ll feel better.

01:08:09.234 --> 01:08:12.167
So you have to correct your ideas

01:08:12.167 --> 01:08:18.567
about marriage, about women,
about men, about yourself.

01:08:18.567 --> 01:08:22.967
That’s very important
because it is a very big emotional thing

01:08:22.967 --> 01:08:27.767
and, as the left side is weak,

01:08:27.767 --> 01:08:31.867
all people who have left side weak get cold.

01:08:31.867 --> 01:08:37.901
And all the things that have to do with your...
they call it bulgam, is it? What’s it called?

01:08:37.901 --> 01:08:38.801
Sahaja Yogis: Phlegm.

01:08:38.801 --> 01:08:45.734
Phlegm. Phlegm. Phlegm.
It has to do with your phlegm.

01:08:45.734 --> 01:08:52.801
So the emotional side is to be properly nourished and looked after

01:08:52.801 --> 01:09:03.434
and one has to know that your dignity is the most important.

01:09:03.434 --> 01:09:10.134
Anything undignified is not love.
Love is very dignified.

01:09:10.134 --> 01:09:18.867
And if you keep your dignity, you’ll be amazed how you will be able to solve certain problems.

01:09:18.867 --> 01:09:23.467
Now, again I’ll ask you a question.
Now, how many have answered the questions?

01:09:23.467 --> 01:09:26.134
Most of them you answered very well.

01:09:26.134 --> 01:09:33.567
Now one more question I will ask.

01:09:33.567 --> 01:09:40.467
Very simple, not so difficult.

01:09:40.467 --> 01:09:47.201
That: what is the difference between a baddha and a bhoot?

01:09:47.201 --> 01:09:57.401
How will you make out? A hindrance and a bhoot.

01:09:57.401 --> 01:10:02.201
Sahaja Yogi: Bhoots will move around.

01:10:02.201 --> 01:10:03.267
And baddha?

01:10:03.267 --> 01:10:07.901
Sahaja Yogi: Stays there. Just describing,
it’s a block at that point.

01:10:07.901 --> 01:10:10.434
Though it’s correct, you said is correct,

01:10:10.434 --> 01:10:16.867
but it is not absolutely precise.
It is like this, I tell you. It’s correct.

01:10:16.867 --> 01:10:20.434
I mean what he says is the correct answer but it’s not so precise.

01:10:20.434 --> 01:10:26.234
Baddha will also move.
I’ll tell you how.

01:10:26.234 --> 01:10:30.334
Baddha is always in the centers or on your organs, say.

01:10:30.334 --> 01:10:35.967
If it is, say, in your, for example in the liver,

01:10:35.967 --> 01:10:39.567
this baddha may come in the center

01:10:39.567 --> 01:10:48.767
and then it will start moving from your here to here as the Kundalini will move. Alright?

01:10:48.767 --> 01:10:55.167
But baddha doesn’t have its arbitrary movement.

01:10:55.167 --> 01:10:57.667
As you move the Kundalini, the baddha moves.

01:10:57.667 --> 01:11:01.134
‘Baddha’ means hindrance. Alright?

01:11:01.134 --> 01:11:06.967
But a bhoot is arbitrary.
It moves.

01:11:06.967 --> 01:11:10.467
It will be one moment here, it will be one moment there.

01:11:10.467 --> 01:11:12.901
It will move this side, it will move that side.

01:11:12.901 --> 01:11:16.467
It will go to the right heart, then it will come to the left heart.

01:11:16.467 --> 01:11:19.667
If it is arbitrary behaviour,

01:11:19.667 --> 01:11:25.801
that means it is not controlled by your movement of your fingers through the Kundalini awakening

01:11:25.801 --> 01:11:29.534
that means it is not controlled by your movement of your fingers through the Kundalini awakening

01:11:29.534 --> 01:11:32.867
Now understand what I’m saying by decisive thing,

01:11:32.867 --> 01:11:37.367
that, one thing is arbitrary, works on its own,

01:11:37.367 --> 01:11:46.000
and the other is in your control.
You’re taking it out yourself.

01:11:46.000 --> 01:11:51.101
Like you can say that if there’s some lump in the body,

01:11:51.101 --> 01:11:54.934
it may start moving with the, say, bloodstream or something,

01:11:54.934 --> 01:11:59.601
some force acting upon it.
But by itself, it does not.

01:11:59.601 --> 01:12:06.767
But if there’s a worm, a living worm, it will move by itself.

01:12:06.767 --> 01:12:17.401
So the last question is then,
how do you manage the baddha and the bhoot?

01:12:17.401 --> 01:12:21.667
How will you take out the bhoot of other people without getting yourself into it?

01:12:21.667 --> 01:12:25.667
Otherwise the person whose bhoot has to be taken out

01:12:25.667 --> 01:12:31.901
will put three bhoots in you and five in the others.

01:12:31.901 --> 01:12:39.734
I have seen many a times they’ll come and tell Me,
“Mother, he’s possessed.” Alright.

01:12:39.734 --> 01:12:47.734
And they themselves are!

01:12:47.734 --> 01:12:52.834
How do you take out? Come along.

01:12:52.834 --> 01:12:54.934
Sahaja Yogini: Bandhan

01:12:54.934 --> 01:12:57.034
Sahaja Yogi: You can throw the bhoot into a candle.

01:12:57.034 --> 01:13:01.201
What? Bandhan? No!

01:13:01.201 --> 01:13:06.267
No, First, first, that of course,
you all know what I’m doing, but…

01:13:06.267 --> 01:13:10.301
Sahaja Yogi: You can throw the bhoot into a candle.

01:13:10.301 --> 01:13:12.801
I mean, I’m saying a real one.

01:13:12.801 --> 01:13:18.000
He’s not even afraid of candles.

01:13:18.000 --> 01:13:25.301
Sahaja Yogini: Say the mantra to Mukti Dayini.

01:13:25.301 --> 01:13:27.034
Sahaja Yogini: The Lord’s Prayer

01:13:27.034 --> 01:13:31.501
There’s no general thing about it.
Alright?

01:13:31.501 --> 01:13:41.701
All answers are correct but they are not complete.

01:13:41.701 --> 01:13:56.067
There are ways and methods according to different bhoots.

01:13:56.067 --> 01:13:58.501
They are trying to solve the problems

01:13:58.501 --> 01:14:08.067
But said it’s rather difficult!

01:14:08.067 --> 01:14:14.901
Now, first of all, you see a person who is possessed.

01:14:14.901 --> 01:14:25.901
I mean you are sure he is possessed, so you do like this, you see.

01:14:25.901 --> 01:14:28.234
Take a form, you have to take a form

01:14:28.234 --> 01:14:32.067
because you have to fight it.
You take an aggressive form.

01:14:32.067 --> 01:14:37.501
Sahaja Yogi: Karate, Tony’s Karate [Tony Cooly].

01:14:37.501 --> 01:14:39.934
Karate, yes. Something like that.

01:14:39.934 --> 01:14:46.367
So then, I mean inside you become higher than that person.

01:14:46.367 --> 01:14:56.167
Otherwise if you go like

01:14:56.167 --> 01:15:00.401
After some time

01:15:00.401 --> 01:15:06.667
So you go with a great force on that person.

01:15:06.667 --> 01:15:10.767
You put a bandhan and say, “Now sit down.”
Talk to him like this.

01:15:10.767 --> 01:15:13.734
You don’t go and say, “Please sit down,”

01:15:13.734 --> 01:15:17.201
because the thing will come and sit in you.

01:15:17.201 --> 01:15:19.567
Just say, “Now sit down.” Alright.

01:15:19.567 --> 01:15:25.467
There you have to say as if you are not compromising on this.

01:15:25.467 --> 01:15:28.334
No compromises.

01:15:28.334 --> 01:15:35.667
Then you ask the person various questions,
after giving yourself a bandhan

01:15:35.667 --> 01:15:41.401
and do that to verify what sort of a bhoot it could be.
That’s the best.

01:15:41.401 --> 01:15:46.467
First of all you ask that person,
“Have you been to any guru?”

01:15:46.467 --> 01:15:53.000
So now you know at least sixteen of them.
And you know how to take them out, also.

01:15:53.000 --> 01:15:57.934
So you find out which bhoot he has been to.

01:15:57.934 --> 01:16:02.301
If it is a guru, you just ask the person
does he still believe in that guru.

01:16:02.301 --> 01:16:04.867
If so, you have nothing to do with that person.

01:16:04.867 --> 01:16:07.201
You have no business.
You say, “I’m sorry, sir” …

01:16:07.201 --> 01:16:11.167
Not sorry You say, “Please go away.”

01:16:11.167 --> 01:16:13.534
If you say “sorry” it will come inside.

01:16:13.534 --> 01:16:18.167
Any inviting word you should not use.

01:16:18.167 --> 01:16:24.101
Just say, “Alright, finished!” you get out from that one.

01:16:24.101 --> 01:16:26.967
But in case he says, “I am possessed.
I know I am in trouble,

01:16:26.967 --> 01:16:31.867
I’ve got this thing” and all that,
then you tell that person that

01:16:31.867 --> 01:16:36.101
“What is the name of your guru? What is the mantra you got?

01:16:36.101 --> 01:16:39.767
How many years have you been?”
Like that, you ask the question.

01:16:39.767 --> 01:16:41.967
If he is truthful and if he tells you that,

01:16:41.967 --> 01:16:47.501
then you exactly know where the mantra is,
what has happened to him.

01:16:47.501 --> 01:16:53.767
If it is a guru, then it has to be in the Void.

01:16:53.767 --> 01:17:03.201
If it is in the Void you tell him to say the mantra of Adi Guru,

01:17:03.201 --> 01:17:07.767
or ask the question, “Mother, are You the…?” on the photograph.

01:17:07.767 --> 01:17:12.267
Keep the photograph in front of your face like a mask if possible.

01:17:12.267 --> 01:17:16.201
Don’t allow you yourself to be exposed but give the photograph to the man.

01:17:16.201 --> 01:17:20.167
You say, “Now ask the question to this photograph.”

01:17:20.167 --> 01:17:25.534
Now if the person asks the question, the Kundalini
will start coming here doing

01:17:25.534 --> 01:17:30.000
“gragaralgagal.” He’ll also see the thing there,
you see, bubbling up.

01:17:30.000 --> 01:17:37.334
Then you should say that, after asking the question, “Now you say that, ‘You are the guru’!”

01:17:37.334 --> 01:17:41.301
If the person is possessed by a guru, then if you know the name of the guru,

01:17:41.301 --> 01:17:43.767
then you know the mantra.
When he’s doing all these things,

01:17:43.767 --> 01:17:47.534
you go on saying “NarakasuraMardini”
or “Mahishasura Mardini”

01:17:47.534 --> 01:17:52.767
or anything like that, whatever you have to do.
Or “Sarva-asura Mardini”

01:17:52.767 --> 01:17:58.067
For guru this thing, the best thing is salt, vibrated salt.

01:17:58.067 --> 01:18:02.534
You give some vibrated salt with water to that person to drink.

01:18:02.534 --> 01:18:07.167
It’s not easy to get rid of the guru, so you tell him very firmly

01:18:07.167 --> 01:18:10.867
that he’s one of the horrible ones we have ever known,

01:18:10.867 --> 01:18:13.667
so you have to work very hard to get rid of it.

01:18:13.667 --> 01:18:20.734
You give him salt, give him all that, let him do it.
And do not hurry up.

01:18:20.734 --> 01:18:24.301
Tell him it is going to take time, it will be alright,

01:18:24.301 --> 01:18:26.267
and what troubles people had with this,

01:18:26.267 --> 01:18:29.401
and he’ll have to work hard.

01:18:29.401 --> 01:18:33.567
This is one type of bhoots you will find.

01:18:33.567 --> 01:18:39.234
Then you find these are guru bhoots and which takes time,

01:18:39.234 --> 01:18:44.301
which are very difficult and they can take you up,

01:18:44.301 --> 01:18:47.067
it can be very dangerous.

01:18:47.067 --> 01:18:54.401
But say, somebody becomes blind with a bhoot.

01:18:54.401 --> 01:18:56.501
His eyes are open and he’s blind.

01:18:56.501 --> 01:19:05.601
That’s sure shot he is blind because of a bhoot.
Two types of blindness are possible.

01:19:05.601 --> 01:19:12.534
The Left Swadhishthana will be catching
and you will see it is due to bhoot.

01:19:12.534 --> 01:19:15.034
But it can also be Left Swadhisthana catching

01:19:15.034 --> 01:19:20.434
and becoming blind could be with diabetes.

01:19:20.434 --> 01:19:22.934
Could be the combination of both.

01:19:22.934 --> 01:19:25.034
So you ask him if he has diabetes or not.

01:19:25.034 --> 01:19:29.434
If the person has no diabetes, then definitely it is the bhoot.

01:19:29.434 --> 01:19:37.401
Now what do you do to take out that kind of a bhoot?

01:19:37.401 --> 01:19:39.401
Sahaja Yogi: You use an enlightened candle.

01:19:39.401 --> 01:19:43.467
You take My hand.

01:19:43.467 --> 01:19:48.401
Photograph, only hand.

01:19:48.401 --> 01:19:52.667
You have photographs of My hand,
and put a candle before that photograph.

01:19:52.667 --> 01:19:57.534
All these photographs that you have separately have meanings.

01:19:57.534 --> 01:20:03.967
Put the candle and behind that is the hand

01:20:03.967 --> 01:20:08.534
and ask the person to see the light,
if he can see the light.

01:20:08.534 --> 01:20:13.101
Gradually, you’ll be amazed he will start seeing.

01:20:13.101 --> 01:20:15.901
This is to be used.
You see, in Sahaja Yoga,

01:20:15.901 --> 01:20:19.467
one has also to be precise just like the English words.

01:20:19.467 --> 01:20:21.867
If you are precise, it comes out.

01:20:21.867 --> 01:20:26.201
If you are not precise then you try this, you try that, it won’t work out.

01:20:26.201 --> 01:20:29.467
But if you have a photograph of My hands

01:20:29.467 --> 01:20:38.301
you should ask the person to see the photograph of the hand.

01:20:38.301 --> 01:20:43.367
By seeing the light, gradually the person will start seeing the hand,

01:20:43.367 --> 01:20:46.367
and then gradually the person will become alright.

01:20:46.367 --> 01:20:52.801
I’ve seen one person getting the eyes within ten minutes.

01:20:52.801 --> 01:20:55.667
But in that, if the Left Swadhishthana is catching,

01:20:55.667 --> 01:20:59.567
if the person has no diabetes and eyes are open,

01:20:59.567 --> 01:21:03.167
then it is definitely a bhoot, nothing else.

01:21:03.167 --> 01:21:06.201
Even if some people might say, “She lost her eyes because of,

01:21:06.201 --> 01:21:09.534
this girl lost her eyes because there was a fire in the house.”

01:21:09.534 --> 01:21:14.101
But she got frightened and the bhoots sat in here and she became blind. They are connected to both things.

01:21:14.101 --> 01:21:18.467
Actually eyes cannot remain open if the eyes are burned out.

01:21:18.467 --> 01:21:21.267
So if the eyes are open and absolutely normal to look at

01:21:21.267 --> 01:21:23.367
and the person cannot see, the light is out,

01:21:23.367 --> 01:21:26.567
that means there’s a bhoot.

01:21:26.567 --> 01:21:30.601
So these things can be very easily done.

01:21:30.601 --> 01:21:36.101
Sahaja Yogi: How do you do it?

01:21:36.101 --> 01:21:39.634
Photograph like this, and the light in front.

01:21:39.634 --> 01:21:41.467
It will improve your eyesight also.

01:21:41.467 --> 01:21:46.267
My hands should be used, very good for the eyes.

01:21:46.267 --> 01:21:50.234
My hands are extremely good for your eyes.

01:21:50.234 --> 01:21:53.767
If you can see My hands with the light,

01:21:53.767 --> 01:21:57.534
very good for your eyes.

01:21:57.534 --> 01:22:07.534
Now what are good My feet for?

